SHREK TIME
///22 APR 2001 --- Dawn of Shrek Time
1 SH = 1.5hrs (rounded)
1 SHREK DAY (SD) = 18 HRS

1 SHREK MONTH = 487 SH (5488/12 = 487) ~(27SH) (0.6672 SH each year extra)
1 YEAR = 5844 SH

